About Us

MechCat (short for MeCATronics) is a first-year team consisting of Grade 12 students from Dr. Norman Bethune C.I. In spite of our inexperience, we’ve continued to climb our way over each obstacle with determination and spirit. The memories we’ve collectively made as a team has helped us assemble a tight-knitted group that share the same ignited passion for robotics.
